oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 11th Annual Nashville Unlimited Christmas Concert (2010)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Concerts; music festivals; Christmas; Harris, Emmylou; Miller, Buddy;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red on green) announcing the 11th Annual Christmas Concert with Emmylou Harris, Buddy Miller, Mike Farris and the McCrary Sisters, Three Ring Circle, Duffy Jackson Big Band, Vinnie Vidivici, and others at the Christ Church Cathedral on December 15. Event benefits the Room For An Inn.
